name: Jesus
aboutpara:
In the first proyect, i developed an AI-powered web application providing visual cues for autistic individuals with low to medium support needs.  Using a quantitative approach and XP methodology, the project focused on designing a didactic tool to improve communication and comprehension. 

in the second proyect, I developed a CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) web application for managing real estate information.  Using a quantitative approach and agile methodologies, the project focused on designing a system to keep property details organized and easily accessible, thereby improving data management and search efficiency.

in the third project, I developed an API for a class on quantitative methods.  Using a quantitative approach and an iterative development process, the project focused on designing an efficient API to provide statistical functions and data analysis for academic purposes.
